ext=\"x\"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>-axis. A triangle is formed by the points at the origin,&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\"><semantics><mi>P</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>, and&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"Q\"><math alttext=\"Q\"><semantics><mi>Q</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>. The function&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\"><semantics><mi>A</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;gives the area of the triangle,&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"A open parentheses theta close parentheses\"><math alttext=\"A open parentheses theta close parentheses\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mfenced><mi>θ</mi></mfenced></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>, based on the measure of the angle&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"theta\"><math alttext=\"theta\"><semantics><mi>θ</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>, in radians. What is the value of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"A open parentheses pi over 3 close parentheses\"><math alttext=\"A open parentheses pi over 3 close parentheses\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mfenced><mfrac><mi>π</mi><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mfenced></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;? (Note: The area of a triangle with base&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"b\"><math alttext=\"b\"><semantics><mi>b<